One of the best shooters at the academy, Marzé Becker shot 200/200 in the prone position. Gene Moulder, founder of the academy, said they are proud of Marzé and the other shooters from the club who performed well during the competition. He added that their fifth match was a build-up to the open championships scheduled for 25 and 26 June in Vanderbijlpark. “Our last league match will take place on 31 July in preparation for the Limpopo Open on 27 and 28 August. Shooters from Gauteng, Free State and North West will also participate.”